parameters: \n<Dwayne>Pardon us for bothering you. I am Dwayne a Mage from Selpha.
\n<Eli>Ask now for I don't have much time talking to humans.
\n<Dwayne>Gargoyles are taking children and women, where can we find them?
\n<Eli>They can be found in Lucio's World in Basi Island, and
only the Army of Light can defeat Lucio.
\n<Eli>It was written on the last page of my book, "The Knight of Light
will form an Army, they are the Army of Light."
\n<Philip>Can you tell us who they are?
\n<Eli>It is for you to find out.
\n<Zarie>Another question, are you human or just a mirror? I mean, you
don't even look like a mirror.
\n<Eli>I was a human, and now, I am a soul trapped in the mirror of everything. I see
the future, present and past. But, I only choose the questions that I want
\n<Philip>How can we get out of this place?
\n<Eli>I cannot answer that. For centuries, people have come here,
but none of them got out.
\n<Eli>...ENOUGH!!! I am done answering your questions. LEAVE NOW!
Heavy armor, heavy helm and heavy gloves found!
